                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <div class="card-img">
                                <img src="~/images/bull-semen.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-desc">
                                <h3>Bull Semen and Embryos</h3>
                                <hr class="colored">
                                <p>
                                    Our bulls offer strong, diverse pedigrees and a proven track record.
                                </p>
