                            <div class="card-img">
                                <img src="~/images/pork2.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-desc">
                                <h3>Pastured Pork</h3>
                                <hr class="colored">
                                <p>
                                    1/2 and Whole Pig –<br />
                                    $4.15/lb hanging weight<br />
                                    Price includes all butcher costs<br />
                                    Custom cut and vacuum packed
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- About Section -->
<section class="page-section" id="about">
    <section>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="wow fadeIn text-center">
            <h1>WHAT WE DO</h1>
            <p class="mb-0">
                "We work off a platform of integrity – treating our customers the way we would like to be treated. <br />
                Visitors are always welcome, and we enjoy helping other farmers get started or improve their herds.<br />
                Please contact us and see if we can fit the needs of your herd or to just talk about Devon cattle."<br />
                -Bob VanKirk
            </p>
            <hr class="colored">
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                    <div class="wow fadeIn px-4 pb-4 pb-lg-0 h-100" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                        <i class="fa fa-cutlery fa-4x"></i>
                        <h3>100% Grass Fed Beef</h3>
                        <p class="mb-0"><strong>NO</strong> Hormones <br> <strong>NO</strong> Antibiotics <br><strong>NO</strong> Animal Byproducts</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                    <div class="wow fadeIn px-4 pb-4 pb-lg-0 h-100" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                        <i class="fa fa-users fa-4x"></i>
                        <h3>Family Owned Business</h3>
                        <p class="mb-0">Bob grew up on a beef farm and has enjoyed developing his own herd of now 100 Registered Devons. Employing his son Robert, 4 Seasons Farm provides quality beef with service you'd only expect from a family owned business.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

